8.1.2 搜索关键词按类别画词云
data2=data1[data1$action=='query',]
data2=data2[order(data2$obj),]
category=read.csv('C:\\Users\\guquan\\Desktop\\my\\结构图\\tree.csv',header=T,stringsAsFactors=F)

#data2：关键词匹配对应大类
t2=table(data2$obj)
u2=unique(data2$obj)
data2$cate='a'
sum=1
for(i in 1:length(u2)){
  for(j in 1:nrow(category))
    if(category$kw[j]==u2[i]){
      data2$cate[sum:(sum+as.numeric(t2[i])-1)]=category$'大类'[j]
      break
    }
  sum=sum+as.numeric(t2[i])    
}

data3=data2[data2$cate!='a',c('obj','cate')]
#data4：去重
data4=unique(data3)
data4$freq=as.numeric(table(data3$obj))


data5=data4[order(data4$cate),]
dm=array(rep(0,nrow(data5)*5),dim=c(nrow(data5),5))
t5=as.numeric(table(data5$cate))

#构造分类-词频矩阵
s=1
for(i in 1:5){
  dm[s:(s+t5[i]-1),i]=data5$freq[s:(s+t5[i]-1)]
  s=s+t5[i]
}
colnames(dm)=unique(data5$cate)
row.names(dm)=data5$obj

8.3 分时段搜索行为统计

#读取数据
df=read.csv('C:\\Users\\guquan\\Desktop\\my\\wzx_g_20160519-25.csv',header=T,stringsAsFactors=F)
#定义一个计算view和query的函数
vi_and_que <- function(data){
  data$time = as.POSIXct(data$timestamps/1000, origin="1970-01-01 00:00:00")
  data$hour = as.numeric(substr(as.character(data$time),12,13))
  view=c(1:24)
  query=c(1:24)
  for(i in 1:24){
    view[i]=dim(filter(data,hour==i-1&action=='view'))[1]
    query[i]=dim(filter(data,hour==i-1&action=='query'))[1]
  }
  return(cbind(view,query))
}

#分开计算
da=list();db=list()
for(i in 1:7){
  da[[i]]=df[df$input_day==(20160518+i),]
  db[[i]]=cbind(vi_and_que(da[[i]]),hour=c(1:24),day=rep(518+i,24))
}

#合并
df_all=db[[1]]
for(i in 1:6){
  df_all=rbind(df_all,db[[i+1]])
}

#拉长
df_all1=melt(as.data.frame(df_all),id=c('hour','day'))

#作图
echartR(df_all1, x= ~hour, y= ~value, series= ~variable, z= ~day, type='linesmooth',
        pos=list(title=12,toolbox=3),title='当日浏览/搜索次数统计',
        palette='tableauPrGy', xlab = 'Hour', ylab = '次数',
        yAxis=list(banded=T))
